{"tid":779493,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"《大行報告》大摩相信舜宇(02382.HK)股價30日內將跌","createTime":"2018-08-14T12:22:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T04:00:44.000Z","uid":91648,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7bd21fc218bb1f5545b4b2da139a3b1f6bfced19","tid":779493,"uid":91648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T12:22:21.000Z","msg":"《大行報告》大摩相信舜宇(<a href=\"http://02382.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F02382.HK&d=DrYW53ZiRSe9wNmx%2B8wU6mi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=b1cccffc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">02382.HK</a>)股價30日內將跌<br />\n關閉<br />\n<strong>2018/08/14 10:14  </strong>沽空資料   股價升跌<br />\n <br />\n摩根士丹利發表技術意見報告，相信舜宇光學(<a href=\"http://02382.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F02382.HK&d=DrYW53ZiRSe9wNmx%2B8wU6mi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=b1cccffc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">02382.HK</a>)  -29.200 (-24.112%)    沽空 $6.99億; 比率 11.091%   於未來30日股價下跌，料發生概率介乎70%-80%。<br />\n<br />\n該行指，由於舜宇上半年盈利低於該行預測19%，並低於市場預測22%，反映市場競爭激烈及人民幣貶值因素，該行相信市場須重整對舜宇手機鏡頭模組利潤率的期望，有關因素主要影響其業務表現，該行計算利潤率每下降1個百分點，對每股盈利的影響達10%。而大摩對舜宇最新評級「與大市同步」，目標價120元。(vi/w)(報價延遲最少十五分鐘。沽空資料截至 2018-08-14 16:25。)"},{"pid":"439ed46418ec685fa3a915e6dc1f612b2d9eaa43","tid":779493,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T12:23:11.000Z","msg":"今日咪跌左囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21f5c69be65e80066f4f1ba61b607afa775f54e7","tid":779493,"uid":102198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T12:34:35.000Z","msg":"中牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d03456ae710f521387657a7d5eb8f3bc3f97c8","tid":779493,"uid":171816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T12:49:04.000Z","msg":"好撚準<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff90c7f56f8080f541cfe4c8043d63